To automatically generate a table of contents in a LaTeX document, follow these steps:

\begin{enumerate}
    \item Add the \texttt{\usepackage{hyperref}} package to the preamble of your document. This package is necessary for creating hyperlinks in the table of contents.
    \item Use the \texttt{\tableofcontents} command at the desired location in your document. This command will automatically generate a table of contents based on the section headings in your document.
